<author>hạny rwmạny, mạhr fạyz</author>
<title>mạl ạ̹ly wsmʿ ṣrạkẖy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mạl ạ̹ly wsmʿ ṣrạkẖy .. ʿwḍ ṣbry wạntẓạry
 ạ̉kẖrj rjly mn ạlsẖbkẗ .. hạʿln frḥy wlyh ạ̉dạry
 1- yạ mạ sẖʿrt bạ̹ny wḥyd .. wạ̹n kẖlạṣy mnạlh bʿyd
 smʿ ạlfạdy ạ̉nyny fy .. kẖby̱ ʿly ftylty ạlmṭfyẗ
 (rḥmth sạʿt kl ʿywby)3 .. wnfkẖ fy ʿmr jdyd
 2- ṭwby̱ llmtkl ʿlyh .. tttẖbt kẖṭwạt rjlyh
 knt fy wạdy ạlmwt bṣrkẖ lh .. qlby jryḥ myn yrạ̉f byh
 (jạny mlạny bqwẗ rwḥh)3 .. wjh ạlywm ạlly ạ̉frḥ fyh
 3- kẖly ạltrnym mạly kyạny .. wạltsbyḥ rạyty wʿnwạny
 wyqwlwạ dạ ạ̹lhh ʿjyb .. lạ ytrk ạ̹ymạnh ykẖyb
 (myn ạlrạʿy ạlly byrʿạh)3 wyḥwl nwḥh lạ̉gẖạny</lyrics>
</song>